title: Domain
text: We use the horizontal extent of the graph to find the domain of the function.

title: Domain
text: What is the horizontal extent of the graph? Express it in the form of interval. We can use a symbol known as the union, U, to combine the two sets.

title: Range
text: We use the vertical extent of the graph to find the range of the function.

title: Range
text: What is the vertical extent of the graph? Express it in the form of interval. We can use a symbol known as the union, U, to combine the two sets.
